sentences: Kurumi Enomoto (榎本 くるみ, Enomoto Kurumi, born 17 October 1981), formerly known as Kurumi (くるみ), is a Japanese singer-songwriter.
She debuted in 2002 with the independently released single Moeru Taiyō (燃える太陽, Burning Sun).
